{"tid":1725224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我想搵返頭先坐喺我樓下喊左兩個鐘既女仔！","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:39:23.000Z","uid":15716,"like":10,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"65ab32e36288634a692c250f1b9de58029aa805e","tid":1725224,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"頭先體感16度既你喺我樓下坐左兩個鐘，我問你佢住邊你話佢同我住同一橦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶你去站既時候問左你一條問題，放低一個人要幾耐 <br />\n你話我都唔知，自自然然就會唔記得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傾計既時間唔多同唔到你講以下既說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講，雖然你而家仲好傷心好唔捨得佢，但當你第時回望返今晚既你，你會覺得好傻好白痴<br />\n點解要自己凍住坐喺度兩個鐘去奢望一個唔會落嚟見你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你可以快啲放低佢，唔好再喺我樓下喊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然你可能sem議員，但都希望你可以忘記咗佢專心讀書，祝你快啲上返大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a330866d010a01261d0c4e6f8ee8c73825a64d0","tid":1725224,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55918314fc9e6ff9e6faf1ef3b00d85ef453aa4","tid":1725224,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"等佢嗰陣睇下我篇文<br />\n<br />\n唔該想知中大發生咩事就入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea88e75133baa86a7470b90e03581bfad3722095","tid":1725224,"uid":214036,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e78bd19c9e1e5f4ceb96d064279d5bf33b4c815","tid":1725224,"uid":15716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ea88e75133baa86a7470b9